      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "The feeling of being a glitch rather than a vital part of a story is incredibly isolating, and it makes sense that you feel more comfortable through absence than confusion. While the idea that you are a mistake might sound comforting in its simplicity, your experiences shape the future even if no one can fully see you in the moment. Please talk to someone you trust about this heaviness, because carrying that weight alone often leads to silence, which doesn't make the noise disappear.",
