      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it's just that silence you're talking about... it doesn't feel heavy. it feels like relief. like if i just slipped away, there wouldn't be this constant pressure to perform being a person. it wouldn't be a tragedy if no one even noticed i was gone. it'd just be peaceful. like a mistake being erased so everything is finally clean again.",
